    exampleBeginner: "1. Set a target at your chosen distance (e.g. 100 m).\n2. Shoot a small group (3–5 shots).\n3. See where the group is relative to the crosshair; turn elevation and windage knobs to move the group to the centre.\n4. When impact = crosshair at that distance, you’re zeroed. Enter that distance in the app as “zero distance”.",
